# Refactoring Massive Components

This plan outlines the steps to refactor `CustomMenuWizardVariant1.tsx` (~4200 LOC) and `MenuConfigPageV3Complete.tsx` (~3600 LOC) into smaller, more manageable modules.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This refactor involves significant movement of code into new files. While the functionality will remain identical, the file structure will change. Please confirm if the proposed directory structure aligns with your project preferences.

## Proposed Changes

### Component: `CustomMenuWizard` Refactor
Goal: Split the giant wizard component into specialized sub-components and hooks.

#### [NEW] [types.ts](file:///d:/Oliv-Booking-System/components/user/wizard/types.ts)
- Extract all interfaces like `EventDetails`, `MenuItem`, `AddonGroup`, etc.

#### [NEW] [useWizardCart.ts](file:///d:/Oliv-Booking-System/components/user/wizard/hooks/useWizardCart.ts)
- Extract cart management logic: `toggleMenuItem`, `updateQuantity`, `removeFromCart`.
- Extract pricing calculations: `getTotalPrice`, `getItemTotalPrice`, `getTotalPriceWithAddOns`.

#### [NEW] [Step1Form.tsx](file:///d:/Oliv-Booking-System/components/user/wizard/components/Step1Form.tsx)
- Extract the event details form logic and UI.

#### [NEW] [CategorySection.tsx](file:///d:/Oliv-Booking-System/components/user/wizard/components/CategorySection.tsx)
- Extract the menu category selection and item listing.

#### [MODIFY] [CustomMenuWizardVariant1.tsx](file:///d:/Oliv-Booking-System/components/user/CustomMenuWizardVariant1.tsx)
- Orchestrate the sub-components and use the new hooks.
- Reduce file size to < 500 LOC.

